{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Art of The Invincible</h2><br>The journey to <strong>Regis III</strong> is a feast for the eyes thanks to the creativity and talent that's flowing through the artists and designers at <strong>Starward Industries</strong> studio. Take a behind-the-scenes look at its creation and witness the various stages of the creative process that brought it to life.<br><br>The <strong>digital artbook</strong> contains sketches, concept art, and illustrations used during the game's development. Stylized characters, atompunk robots, tools, and alien landscapes await you, all based on a precisely defined retro-futuristic aesthetic that pays homage to the era in which the iconic novel <strong>'The Invincible' by Stanis\u0142aw Lem</strong> was written.<br><br>The artbook also includes a digital version of <strong>'The Invincible' comic book </strong>- a side story intertwined with the narrative of the game, conceived by <strong>Maciej Dobrowolski</strong>, <strong>Olga Piech</strong>, and <strong>Wojciech Ostrycharz</strong>. Beautiful, iconic illustrations by <strong>Wojciech Ostrycharz</strong> and <strong>Agnieszka Szczeliniak</strong> will help you immerse yourself in the mysterious and philosophical atmosphere of <strong>Starward Industries </strong> game.<br><br>The product also contains 2 additional skin sets to customize your Rover.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1720103815","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622920/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1720103815","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622920/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1720103815","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622920/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1720103815","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},